snippet.title: Foodka Series
snippet.description: Foodka as the name suggests, essentially a series on food. The series will depict food in a non-traditional way. The channel aims to mix food with travel, heritage, culture and represents them with a signature wit. Foodka is a story of a foodie uncle (Foodka ) and his hungry nephew. Foodka is an authority in food who takes his nephew to a gastronomic journey. Foodka essentially starts from Kolkata, the "city of joy" which is also a "city of food". But eventually Foodka will travel across India. Foodka also offers a certification for restaurants and eateries where "Foodka Certified" stands for higher quality, fame and authenticity. The Channel Foodka is a produced by "HungryBaaj Media" and promoted by Anonymous Digital. The product is conceived by Mir Afsar Ali, one of India's most popular RJ, food blogger Indrajit Lahiri and entrepreneur Sunando Banerjee.
